            <article>

                <h3>💧 Drink More Water</h3>

                <p>
                    Water keeps our body hydrated and helps us stay fresh and focused.
                    Drinking 6–8 glasses of water every day is a healthy habit.
                </p>

            </article>

            <article>

                <h3>🏃 Exercise Every Day</h3>

                <p>
                    Walking, cycling, playing outdoor games, or doing yoga for at least
                    30 minutes every day keeps our body strong and healthy.
                </p>

            </article>

